39#ifndef O_DIR_H
40# define O_DIR_H
41
42typedef struct OPENSSL_dir_context_st OPENSSL_DIR_CTX;
43
44/*
45 * returns NULL on error or end-of-directory. If it is end-of-directory,
46 * errno will be zero
47 */
48const char *OPENSSL_DIR_read(OPENSSL_DIR_CTX **ctx, const char *directory);
49/* returns 1 on success, 0 on error */
50int OPENSSL_DIR_end(OPENSSL_DIR_CTX **ctx);
51
52#endif /* LPDIR_H */
